      <h2>How to dial in espresso without wasting a whole bag</h2>
      <p>
        If you’re new to espresso, here’s the part nobody says out loud: your grinder isn’t the only thing changing.
        Your beans change. Your puck prep (that’s just how you load and tamp the grounds) changes. Even your mood
        changes. So you need a simple loop that keeps you sane.
