      <h2>What if you decide you’re done with hand grinding?</h2>
      <p>
        That’s normal. Hand grinding espresso can be a fun ritual, but it can also become a chore if you’re making
        multiple drinks a day. If you start feeling that “I hate this” vibe, don’t blame yourself. It’s just the wrong
        tool for your routine.
